modDescription:
Dungeon Blocks addon that contain 2 spaceship (POI) and a food replicator – hail the gods!

**Required mod:** [Dungeon Blocks](https://7daystodiemods.com/dungeon-blocks/)

## Manuell Installation

1. Download and unpack the Zip data.
2. Place it into your “Mods” folder.
3. Have fun!
4. (optional) Replace and rename the files for Navezgane (inside) to have fix positions and spawnpoints.
5. (optional) Place them manuell as you like.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/EihwazDE/7D2D/-/archive/master/7D2D-master.zip?path=Dungeon%20Blocks%20GSS%20Bifroest)**
